    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="PSA 20:1" />Que l'Éternel te réponde <char style="w" strong="H1732">au</char> jour <char style="w" strong="H4210">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H1732">la</char> détresse; que <char style="w" strong="H1732">le</char> nom du Dieu <char style="w" strong="H4210">de</char> Jacob te mette <char style="w" strong="H1732">en</char> une haute retraite! <verse eid="PSA 20:1" /><verse number="2" style="v" sid="PSA 20:2" /><char style="w" strong="H3117">Qu'il</char> t'envoie <char style="w" strong="H3117">son</char> <char style="w" strong="H6030">secours</char> <char style="w" strong="H3117">du</char> saint lieu, <char style="w" strong="H6030">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H3117">qu'il</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">te</char> soutienne <char style="w" strong="H3117">de</char> Sion! <verse eid="PSA 20:2" /><verse number="3" style="v" sid="PSA 20:3" /><char style="w" strong="H6726">Qu'il</char> <char style="w" strong="H6726">se</char> souvienne <char style="w" strong="H7971">de</char> toutes <char style="w" strong="H7971">tes</char> offrandes <char style="w" strong="H7971">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H6726">qu'il</char> ait <char style="w" strong="H7971">pour</char> agréable <char style="w" strong="H5582">ton</char> holocauste! Sélah (pause). <verse eid="PSA 20:3" /><verse number="4" style="v" sid="PSA 20:4" /><char style="w" strong="H5930">Qu'il</char> t'accorde <char style="w" strong="H2142">le</char> désir <char style="w" strong="H4503">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H2142">ton</char> cœur, <char style="w" strong="H4503">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H5930">qu'il</char> accomplisse <char style="w" strong="H3605">tous</char> <char style="w" strong="H1878">tes</char> desseins! <verse eid="PSA 20:4" /><verse number="5" style="v" sid="PSA 20:5" />Nous triompherons <char style="w" strong="H4390">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H5414">ta</char> délivrance, <char style="w" strong="H3824">et</char> nous élèverons l'étendard <char style="w" strong="H5414">au</char> nom <char style="w" strong="H4390">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H5414">notre</char> Dieu; l'Éternel accomplira <char style="w" strong="H5414">toutes</char> <char style="w" strong="H5414">tes</char> demandes. <verse eid="PSA 20:5" /><verse number="6" style="v" sid="PSA 20:6" />Déjà je sais que l'Éternel <char style="w" strong="H3068">a</char> <char style="w" strong="H3444">délivré</char> <char style="w" strong="H4390">son</char> Oint; <char style="w" strong="H3068">il</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">lui</char> répondra <char style="w" strong="H3068">des</char> cieux <char style="w" strong="H8034">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">sa</char> sainteté, <char style="w" strong="H3068">par</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">le</char> <char style="w" strong="H3444">secours</char> puissant <char style="w" strong="H8034">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">sa</char> droite. <verse eid="PSA 20:6" /><verse number="7" style="v" sid="PSA 20:7" /><char style="w" strong="H3068">Les</char> uns <char style="w" strong="H3068">se</char> vantent <char style="w" strong="H3068">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H8064">leurs</char> chars, <char style="w" strong="H6030">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">les</char> autres <char style="w" strong="H3068">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H8064">leurs</char> chevaux; <char style="w" strong="H3588">mais</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">nous</char>, <char style="w" strong="H3225">du</char> nom <char style="w" strong="H3068">de</char> l'Éternel, <char style="w" strong="H3588">notre</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">Dieu</char>. <verse eid="PSA 20:7" /><verse number="8" style="v" sid="PSA 20:8" />Ils ont plié <char style="w" strong="H3068">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">sont</char> tombés, mais <char style="w" strong="H3068">nous</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">nous</char> sommes relevés <char style="w" strong="H3068">et</char> affermis. <verse eid="PSA 20:8" /><verse number="9" style="v" sid="PSA 20:9" />Éternel, sauve <char style="w" strong="H6965">le</char> roi! Exauce-nous <char style="w" strong="H5307">au</char> jour où nous t'invoquons!<verse eid="PSA 20:9" /></para>
