    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="PSA 30:1" />Je t'exalte, ô Éternel! Car tu m'as relevé, <char style="w" strong="H1004">et</char> tu n'as pas permis <char style="w" strong="H1004">que</char> mes ennemis <char style="w" strong="H1732">se</char> réjouissent <char style="w" strong="H1004">à</char> mon sujet. <verse eid="PSA 30:1" /><verse number="2" style="v" sid="PSA 30:2" /><char style="w" strong="H3068">Éternel</char>, <char style="w" strong="H3068">mon</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">Dieu</char>, <char style="w" strong="H3588">j'ai</char> crié <char style="w" strong="H3068">à</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">toi</char>, <char style="w" strong="H3068">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H3588">tu</char> m'as guéri. <verse eid="PSA 30:2" /><verse number="3" style="v" sid="PSA 30:3" /><char style="w" strong="H3068">Éternel</char>, tu as <char style="w" strong="H3068">fait</char> remonter <char style="w" strong="H3068">mon</char> âme <char style="w" strong="H3068">du</char> Sépulcre; tu m'as rappelé <char style="w" strong="H3068">à</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">la</char> vie, d'entre ceux <char style="w" strong="H3068">qui</char> descendent <char style="w" strong="H7768">vers</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">la</char> fosse. <verse eid="PSA 30:3" /><verse number="4" style="v" sid="PSA 30:4" />Chantez <char style="w" strong="H3068">à</char> l'Éternel, <char style="w" strong="H3068">vous</char>, <char style="w" strong="H5927">ses</char> bien-aimés, <char style="w" strong="H5927">et</char> célébrez <char style="w" strong="H5927">la</char> mémoire <char style="w" strong="H5927">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H3381">sa</char> sainteté! <verse eid="PSA 30:4" /><verse number="5" style="v" sid="PSA 30:5" />Car <char style="w" strong="H3068">il</char> n'y <char style="w" strong="H3068">a</char> qu'un moment dans <char style="w" strong="H3068">sa</char> colère, mais <char style="w" strong="H3068">une</char> vie dans <char style="w" strong="H3068">sa</char> faveur; <char style="w" strong="H3068">les</char> pleurs logent <char style="w" strong="H3068">le</char> soir, <char style="w" strong="H3068">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">le</char> chant <char style="w" strong="H3068">de</char> triomphe revient <char style="w" strong="H3068">le</char> matin. <verse eid="PSA 30:5" /><verse number="6" style="v" sid="PSA 30:6" /><char style="w" strong="H1242">Et</char> moi, <char style="w" strong="H7281">je</char> disais dans <char style="w" strong="H1242">ma</char> prospérité: <char style="w" strong="H7281">Je</char> <char style="w" strong="H2416">ne</char> serai jamais ébranlé! <verse eid="PSA 30:6" /><verse number="7" style="v" sid="PSA 30:7" /><char style="w" strong="H5769">Éternel</char>, par <char style="w" strong="H5769">ta</char> faveur, tu avais établi <char style="w" strong="H5769">la</char> force dans <char style="w" strong="H5769">ma</char> montagne. As-tu caché <char style="w" strong="H5769">ta</char> face? j'ai été tout éperdu. <verse eid="PSA 30:7" /><verse number="8" style="v" sid="PSA 30:8" /><char style="w" strong="H3068">Éternel</char>, <char style="w" strong="H7522">j'ai</char> crié <char style="w" strong="H3068">à</char> <char style="w" strong="H6440">toi</char>; <char style="w" strong="H7522">j'ai</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">fait</char> <char style="w" strong="H5641">ma</char> supplication <char style="w" strong="H3068">à</char> l'Éternel, disant: <verse eid="PSA 30:8" /><verse number="9" style="v" sid="PSA 30:9" />Quel profit retireras-tu <char style="w" strong="H7121">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H7121">mon</char> sang, si <char style="w" strong="H7121">je</char> descends dans <char style="w" strong="H7121">la</char> fosse? <char style="w" strong="H7121">La</char> poussière <char style="w" strong="H3068">te</char> célébrera-t-elle? Annoncera-t-elle ta vérité? <verse eid="PSA 30:9" /><verse number="10" style="v" sid="PSA 30:10" />Éternel, écoute, aie pitié <char style="w" strong="H1818">de</char> moi! Éternel, sois-moi <char style="w" strong="H3381">en</char> aide! <verse eid="PSA 30:10" /><verse number="11" style="v" sid="PSA 30:11" />Tu as changé <char style="w" strong="H3068">mon</char> deuil <char style="w" strong="H3068">en</char> allégresse, tu as délié <char style="w" strong="H8085">le</char> sac <char style="w" strong="H3068">dont</char> j'étais couvert, tu m'as ceint <char style="w" strong="H1961">de</char> joie, <verse eid="PSA 30:11" /><verse number="12" style="v" sid="PSA 30:12" />Afin que ma gloire chante <char style="w" strong="H6605">ta</char> louange, <char style="w" strong="H2015">et</char> ne <char style="w" strong="H8057">se</char> taise point. <verse eid="PSA 30:12" /><verse number="13" style="v" sid="PSA 30:13" /><char style="w" strong="H3068">Éternel</char>, <char style="w" strong="H5769">mon</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">Dieu</char>, je <char style="w" strong="H3068">te</char> <char style="w" strong="H2167">célébrerai</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">à</char> <char style="w" strong="H5769">toujours</char>.<verse eid="PSA 30:13" /></para>
