'abats-tu, <char style="w" strong="H3117">mon</char> âme, <char style="w" strong="H3117">et</char> pourquoi frémis-tu <char style="w" strong="H3117">en</char> moi? Attends-toi <char style="w" strong="H3117">à</char> Dieu, car <char style="w" strong="H3117">je</char> <char style="w" strong="H3117">le</char> louerai <char style="w" strong="H3117">encore</char>; <char style="w" strong="H3117">il</char> <char style="w" strong="H3117">est</char> <char style="w" strong="H3117">mon</char> salut <char style="w" strong="H3117">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H3117">mon</char> Dieu!<verse eid="PSA 42:11" /></para>
