    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="PSA 52:1" />Lorsque Doëg, l'Iduméen, vint avertir Saül, <char style="w" strong="H1732">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H1732">lui</char> dit que <char style="w" strong="H1732">David</char> <char style="w" strong="H1732">s'était</char> rendu <char style="w" strong="H1732">dans</char> <char style="w" strong="H1732">la</char> maison d'Achimélec. <verse eid="PSA 52:1" /><verse number="2" style="v" sid="PSA 52:2" />Pourquoi te glorifies-tu <char style="w" strong="H1004">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H5046">la</char> malice, homme puissant? <char style="w" strong="H5046">La</char> bonté <char style="w" strong="H1004">de</char> Dieu dure toujours. <verse eid="PSA 52:2" /><verse number="3" style="v" sid="PSA 52:3" />Pareille <char style="w" strong="H3117">au</char> rasoir affilé, <char style="w" strong="H3117">ta</char> langue médite <char style="w" strong="H3117">la</char> <char style="w" strong="H3117">ruine</char>, artisan <char style="w" strong="H3117">de</char> fraudes! <verse eid="PSA 52:3" /><verse number="4" style="v" sid="PSA 52:4" />Tu aimes <char style="w" strong="H6213">le</char> <char style="w" strong="H1942">mal</char> <char style="w" strong="H6213">plus</char> <char style="w" strong="H2803">que</char> <char style="w" strong="H6213">le</char> bien, <char style="w" strong="H6213">le</char> mensonge <char style="w" strong="H6213">plus</char> <char style="w" strong="H2803">que</char> <char style="w" strong="H6213">les</char> <char style="w" strong="H3956">paroles</char> justes. Sélah (pause). <verse eid="PSA 52:4" /><verse number="5" style="v" sid="PSA 52:5" />Tu n'aimes <char style="w" strong="H2896">que</char> <char style="w" strong="H1696">les</char> <char style="w" strong="H1696">paroles</char> <char style="w" strong="H2896">de</char> destruction, langue perfide! <verse eid="PSA 52:5" /><verse number="6" style="v" sid="PSA 52:6" /><char style="w" strong="H1697">Aussi</char> <char style="w" strong="H1697">Dieu</char> te détruira <char style="w" strong="H1697">pour</char> toujours; <char style="w" strong="H1697">il</char> te saisira <char style="w" strong="H1697">et</char> t'arrachera <char style="w" strong="H1697">de</char> ta tente; <char style="w" strong="H1697">il</char> te déracinera <char style="w" strong="H1697">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H1697">la</char> terre <char style="w" strong="H1697">des</char> vivants. (Sélah.) <verse eid="PSA 52:6" /><verse number="7" style="v" sid="PSA 52:7" /><char style="w" strong="H5422">Les</char> justes <char style="w" strong="H2416">le</char> verront, <char style="w" strong="H2416">et</char> ils craindront; <char style="w" strong="H2416">et</char> ils <char style="w" strong="H2416">se</char> riront <char style="w" strong="H2416">de</char> lui: <verse eid="PSA 52:7" /><verse number="8" style="v" sid="PSA 52:8" /><char style="w" strong="H7200">Le</char> voilà, cet homme <char style="w" strong="H6662">qui</char> n'avait <char style="w" strong="H7200">point</char> pris Dieu <char style="w" strong="H5921">pour</char> mettait <char style="w" strong="H7200">sa</char> force <char style="w" strong="H7200">dans</char> <char style="w" strong="H7200">sa</char> méchanceté! <verse eid="PSA 52:8" /><verse number="9" style="v" sid="PSA 52:9" />Mais moi, <char style="w" strong="H7760">comme</char> <char style="w" strong="H7760">un</char> olivier verdoyant dans <char style="w" strong="H7760">la</char> maison <char style="w" strong="H7760">à</char> perpétuité. <verse eid="PSA 52:9" /><verse number="10" style="v" sid="PSA 52:10" />Je te louerai <char style="w" strong="H5769">toujours</char>, parce <char style="w" strong="H1004">que</char> tu auras fait cela; <char style="w" strong="H1004">et</char> j'espérerai <char style="w" strong="H5769">en</char> <char style="w" strong="H5769">ton</char> nom, car il <char style="w" strong="H2617">est</char> propice, <char style="w" strong="H5769">en</char> <char style="w" strong="H2617">faveur</char> <char style="w" strong="H1004">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H5769">tes</char> fidèles.<verse eid="PSA 52:10" /></para>
