    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="PSA 140:1" />Éternel, délivre-moi <char style="w" strong="H4210">de</char> l'homme méchant, <char style="w" strong="H1732">et</char> garde-moi <char style="w" strong="H4210">de</char> l'homme violent, <verse eid="PSA 140:1" /><verse number="2" style="v" sid="PSA 140:2" /><char style="w" strong="H3068">Qui</char> méditent <char style="w" strong="H3068">le</char> <char style="w" strong="H7451">mal</char> dans <char style="w" strong="H3068">leur</char> cœur, <char style="w" strong="H3068">et</char> suscitent tous <char style="w" strong="H3068">les</char> jours <char style="w" strong="H3068">des</char> combats; <verse eid="PSA 140:2" /><verse number="3" style="v" sid="PSA 140:3" /><char style="w" strong="H7451">Qui</char> affilent <char style="w" strong="H3117">leur</char> langue <char style="w" strong="H2803">comme</char> <char style="w" strong="H3117">un</char> serpent; <char style="w" strong="H7451">qui</char> ont <char style="w" strong="H3117">un</char> venin d'aspic sous <char style="w" strong="H3117">leurs</char> lèvres. Sélah (pause). <verse eid="PSA 140:3" /><verse number="4" style="v" sid="PSA 140:4" />Éternel, garde-moi <char style="w" strong="H3956">des</char> mains <char style="w" strong="H8193">du</char> méchant, préserve-moi <char style="w" strong="H3956">de</char> l'homme <char style="w" strong="H2534">violent</char>, <char style="w" strong="H8193">qui</char> méditent <char style="w" strong="H3956">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H2534">me</char> faire tomber. <verse eid="PSA 140:4" /><verse number="5" style="v" sid="PSA 140:5" /><char style="w" strong="H3068">Les</char> orgueilleux <char style="w" strong="H3027">m'ont</char> dressé <char style="w" strong="H3068">un</char> <char style="w" strong="H3027">piège</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">des</char> lacs; ils <char style="w" strong="H3027">ont</char> tendu <char style="w" strong="H3068">des</char> rets <char style="w" strong="H3027">sur</char> <char style="w" strong="H8104">le</char> <char style="w" strong="H3027">bord</char> <char style="w" strong="H3027">du</char> chemin; ils <char style="w" strong="H3027">m'ont</char> dressé <char style="w" strong="H3068">des</char> embûches. (Sélah.) <verse eid="PSA 140:5" /><verse number="6" style="v" sid="PSA 140:6" />J'ai dit <char style="w" strong="H3027">à</char> l'Éternel: <char style="w" strong="H3027">Tu</char> es <char style="w" strong="H3027">mon</char> Dieu; prête l'oreille, ô Éternel, <char style="w" strong="H3027">à</char> <char style="w" strong="H3027">la</char> voix <char style="w" strong="H3027">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H6566">mes</char> supplications! <verse eid="PSA 140:6" /><verse number="7" style="v" sid="PSA 140:7" />Seigneur <char style="w" strong="H3068">Éternel</char>, <char style="w" strong="H3068">qui</char> es <char style="w" strong="H3068">la</char> force <char style="w" strong="H6963">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">mon</char> salut, tu as couvert ma tête <char style="w" strong="H3068">au</char> jour <char style="w" strong="H6963">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">la</char> bataille. <verse eid="PSA 140:7" /><verse number="8" style="v" sid="PSA 140:8" /><char style="w" strong="H3069">Éternel</char>, n'accorde pas <char style="w" strong="H3117">au</char> méchant <char style="w" strong="H3117">ses</char> souhaits; <char style="w" strong="H3444">ne</char> fais pas réussir <char style="w" strong="H3117">ses</char> desseins; ils s'élèveraient. (Sélah.) <verse eid="PSA 140:8" /><verse number="9" style="v" sid="PSA 140:9" /><char style="w" strong="H5414">Que</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">sur</char> <char style="w" strong="H5414">la</char> tête <char style="w" strong="H5414">de</char> ceux <char style="w" strong="H3068">qui</char> m'assiègent, retombe l'iniquité <char style="w" strong="H5414">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H5414">leurs</char> lèvres! <verse eid="PSA 140:9" /><verse number="10" style="v" sid="PSA 140:10" />Que <char style="w" strong="H7218">des</char> charbons embrasés tombent sur eux! <char style="w" strong="H5999">Qu'il</char> <char style="w" strong="H3680">les</char> précipite dans <char style="w" strong="H3680">le</char> feu, dans <char style="w" strong="H7218">des</char> flots profonds d'où ils <char style="w" strong="H5999">ne</char> <char style="w" strong="H7218">se</char> relèvent plus! <verse eid="PSA 140:10" /><verse number="11" style="v" sid="PSA 140:11" />L'homme <char style="w" strong="H5307">à</char> <char style="w" strong="H6965">la</char> langue méchante <char style="w" strong="H1077">ne</char> sera <char style="w" strong="H1077">point</char> affermi <char style="w" strong="H5921">sur</char> <char style="w" strong="H6965">la</char> terre; <char style="w" strong="H6965">et</char> quant <char style="w" strong="H5307">à</char> l'homme violent, <char style="w" strong="H6965">le</char> mal <char style="w" strong="H6965">le</char> poursuivra <char style="w" strong="H6965">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H6965">le</char> renversera. <verse eid="PSA 140:11" /><verse number="12" style="v" sid="PSA 140:12" />Je sais <char style="w" strong="H7451">que</char> l'Éternel fera droit <char style="w" strong="H7451">à</char> l'affligé, qu'il fera justice <char style="w" strong="H7451">aux</char> misérables. <verse eid="PSA 140:12" /><verse number="13" style="v" sid="PSA 140:13" />Oui, <char style="w" strong="H6213">les</char> <char style="w" strong="H4941">justes</char> <char style="w" strong="H6213">célébreront</char> <char style="w" strong="H3045">ton</char> nom; <char style="w" strong="H6213">les</char> hommes <char style="w" strong="H1779">droits</char> habiteront devant <char style="w" strong="H6213">ta</char> face.<verse eid="PSA 140:13" /></para>
