    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="PSA 142:1" />Je crie, <char style="w" strong="H4905">de</char> ma voix, <char style="w" strong="H1732">à</char> l'Éternel; <char style="w" strong="H4905">de</char> ma voix, je supplie l'Éternel. <verse eid="PSA 142:1" /><verse number="2" style="v" sid="PSA 142:2" /><char style="w" strong="H6963">Je</char> répands devant <char style="w" strong="H3068">lui</char> ma plainte; j'expose ma détresse <char style="w" strong="H3068">en</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">sa</char> présence. <verse eid="PSA 142:2" /><verse number="3" style="v" sid="PSA 142:3" />Quand <char style="w" strong="H6440">mon</char> esprit <char style="w" strong="H6869">est</char> abattu <char style="w" strong="H6440">en</char> <char style="w" strong="H6440">moi</char>, <char style="w" strong="H6440">toi</char>, <char style="w" strong="H6440">tu</char> connais <char style="w" strong="H6440">mon</char> sentier. <char style="w" strong="H6440">Ils</char> m'ont caché <char style="w" strong="H6440">un</char> piège <char style="w" strong="H6440">dans</char> <char style="w" strong="H6440">le</char> chemin où <char style="w" strong="H6440">je</char> marchais. <verse eid="PSA 142:3" /><verse number="4" style="v" sid="PSA 142:4" />Regarde <char style="w" strong="H3045">à</char> <char style="w" strong="H3045">ma</char> droite, <char style="w" strong="H3045">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H3045">vois</char>! Personne <char style="w" strong="H7307">ne</char> <char style="w" strong="H7307">me</char> <char style="w" strong="H3045">reconnaît</char>; <char style="w" strong="H1980">tout</char> refuge <char style="w" strong="H7307">me</char> manque; personne n'a <char style="w" strong="H3045">souci</char> <char style="w" strong="H7307">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H3045">mon</char> <char style="w" strong="H7307">âme</char>. <verse eid="PSA 142:4" /><verse number="5" style="v" sid="PSA 142:5" />Éternel! <char style="w" strong="H5315">je</char> crie <char style="w" strong="H7200">à</char> <char style="w" strong="H5315">toi</char>, <char style="w" strong="H7200">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H5315">je</char> dis: <char style="w" strong="H7200">Tu</char> es <char style="w" strong="H7200">ma</char> retraite, <char style="w" strong="H7200">mon</char> partage <char style="w" strong="H7200">dans</char> <char style="w" strong="H7200">la</char> terre <char style="w" strong="H7200">des</char> <char style="w" strong="H5315">vivants</char>. <verse eid="PSA 142:5" /><verse number="6" style="v" sid="PSA 142:6" />Sois attentif <char style="w" strong="H3068">à</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">mon</char> <char style="w" strong="H2199">cri</char>, car je suis fort misérable; délivre-moi <char style="w" strong="H2416">de</char> ceux <char style="w" strong="H3068">qui</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">me</char> poursuivent, car ils <char style="w" strong="H3068">sont</char> plus forts <char style="w" strong="H2506">que</char> moi! <verse eid="PSA 142:6" /><verse number="7" style="v" sid="PSA 142:7" /><char style="w" strong="H5337">Retire</char> <char style="w" strong="H5337">mon</char> âme <char style="w" strong="H3966">de</char> sa prison, afin <char style="w" strong="H3588">que</char> <char style="w" strong="H3588">je</char> célèbre <char style="w" strong="H5337">ton</char> nom. <char style="w" strong="H5337">Les</char> justes viendront autour <char style="w" strong="H3966">de</char> moi, parce <char style="w" strong="H3588">que</char> <char style="w" strong="H3588">tu</char> m'auras fait <char style="w" strong="H4480">du</char> <char style="w" strong="H3966">bien</char>.<verse eid="PSA 142:7" /></para>
